- Vâng.

966
01:11:52,805 --> 01:11:53,840
Gwen.

967
01:11:54,040 --> 01:11:55,678
Con đi ngay.

968
01:12:27,006 --> 01:12:28,974
Mình gặp rắc rối to rồi.

969
01:12:52,498 --> 01:12:53,374
Cảm phiền anh ra ngoài

970
01:12:53,533 --> 01:12:55,410
